snippet.title: Stratovarius - S.O.S (Cover)
snippet.description:
Siegfried Song Facebook : http://www.facebook.com/SiegfriedSongOfficial
Alex Nasla Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/alex.nasla
David Olivares Youtube : https://www.youtube.com/user/DavidOlivaresMusic

Hey folks,

I have been living abroad for over 5 years and it has made me quite exhausted and homesick. After I came back from Sweden, I decided to spend time with my family for a year. I have finally returned to my music production while also spending time on numerous covers and originals.

I got an opportunity to work with David Olivares, a young promising guitarist from Chile. You should also check out his dedicated collaborations with lots of musicians on his youtube channel. 

About a month ago, while we recorded this Stratovarius cover, I thought it would sound even better to add a little more perfection for my long awaited fans, so I asked Alex Nasla if we could make some enhancements to the sound with his gorgeous fingers :P And here it is!

We put a lot of effort into this and I believe this could be an enjoyable way to end your year. Alex and I will be back with original material on February. We may also have a couple more covers with David. Until that time, stay tuned!

Merry Christmas and Happy New Year!

Guitars - David Olivares
Keyboards  - Alex Nasla
Vocals - Siegfried Song
Sound Designs - Alex Nasla, David Olivares
Premixing - David Olivares
Mixing and Mastering - Siegfried Song
Filming - Eli Lee, Adam Nasla
Video Editing - Siegfried Song
